  "course_description": "Communication skills are critical to your success at Goizueta. Business Communication Strategy creates the foundation for strong communication & introduces the dynamics of interpersonal & organizational communication. You will create, develop, & deliver professional presentations & documents, individually and in a team. Through the DISC® assessment, you will increase your self-awareness, which helps you identify your most productive communication style.",
